---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — Opawey">
	<main class="min-h-screen bg-white pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
			<p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>

			<div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-neutral-700 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-6">
				<section>
					<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
					<p>By accessing and using the Opawey platform, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">2. Services</h2>
					<p>Opawey provides airport transfer booking, hourly chauffeur rental, tour booking, and experience booking services. We connect passengers with professional licensed drivers.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">3. Booking and Cancellation</h2>
					<p>Bookings are confirmed upon payment or acceptance. Free cancellation is available up to 24 hours before the scheduled pickup time. Cancellations within 24 hours may incur charges.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">4. Payment</h2>
					<p>We accept prepayment via credit/debit card (processed by Stripe), cash on-site, and card on-site (subject to a 5% transaction fee). All prices include VAT, taxes, and tolls unless otherwise stated.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">5. Liability</h2>
					<p>Opawey acts as a platform connecting passengers with drivers. While we vet all drivers and vehicles, we are not liable for delays caused by traffic, weather, or other circumstances beyond our control.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">6. Partner Terms</h2>
					<p>Drivers and partners registering on the platform agree to maintain professional standards, valid insurance, and proper licensing. Opawey retains a 20% commission on all completed rides.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
					<p>For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@opaway.com" class="text-[#0C6B95] hover:underline">info@opaway.com</a>.</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
